<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="mathml.xsl"?><html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xmlns:pref="http://www.w3.org/2002/Math/preference" pref:renderer="mathplayer-dl"><head><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" /><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="opengl-man.css" /><title>modf - OpenGL 4 Shading Language Reference Pages</title><meta name="generator" content="DocBook XSL Stylesheets V1.78.1" /></head><body><div class="refentry"><a id="modf"></a><div class="titlepage"></div><div class="refnamediv"><h2>Name</h2><p>modf — separate a value into its integer and fractional components</p></div><div class="refsynopsisdiv"><h2>Declaration</h2><div class="funcsynopsis"><table border="0" class="funcprototype-table" summary="Function synopsis" style="cellspacing: 0; cellpadding: 0;"><tr><td><code class="funcdef">genType <strong class="fsfunc">modf</strong>(</code></td><td>genType <var class="pdparam">x</var>, </td></tr><tr><td> </td><td>out genType <var class="pdparam">i</var><code>)</code>;</td></tr></table><div class="funcprototype-spacer"> </div></div><div class="funcsynopsis"><table border="0" class="funcprototype-table" summary="Function synopsis" style="cellspacing: 0; cellpadding: 0;"><tr><td><code class="funcdef">genDType <strong class="fsfunc">modf</strong>(</code></td><td>genDType <var class="pdparam">x</var>, </td></tr><tr><td> </td><td>out genDType <var class="pdparam">i</var><code>)</code>;</td></tr></table><div class="funcprototype-spacer"> </div></div></div><div class="refsect1"><a id="parameters"></a><h2>Parameters</h2><div class="variablelist"><dl class="variablelist"><dt><span class="term"><em class="parameter"><code>x</code></em></span></dt><dd><p>
                    Specify the value to separate.
                </p></dd><dt><span class="term"><em class="parameter"><code>out i</code></em></span></dt><dd><p>
                    A variable that receives the integer part of the argument.
                </p></dd></dl></div></div><div class="refsect1"><a id="description"></a><h2>Description</h2><p>
            <code class="function">modf</code> separates a floating point value <em class="parameter"><code>x</code></em>
            into its integer and fractional parts. The fractional part of the number is returned
            from the function and the integer part (as a floating point quantity) is returned
            in the output parameter <em class="parameter"><code>i</code></em>.
        </p></div><div class="refsect1"><a id="versions"></a><h2>Version Support</h2><div class="informaltable"><table border="1"><colgroup><col align="left" /><col align="center" class="firstvers" /><col align="center" /><col align="center" /><col align="center" /><col align="center" /><col align="center" /><col align="center" /><col align="center" /><col align="center" /><col align="center" class="lastvers" /></colgroup><thead><tr><th rowspan="2" align="left">
